snippet.textDisplay: Didn't know that Goalpariya songs are so similar to Bangla. I could understand the lyrics fully, it sounds exactly like Bangla. One of the commenters mentioned that it is an Assamese song derived from the Bengali speaking regions of Assam. I am guessing that it why it is being called an Assamese song but with Bangla lyrics by Papon (again mentioned by one of the commenters). Not sure which one is true, but it is very intriguing.
